XBRate is an engineering tool. It should not be considered a substitute for knowledge, judgement, or experience.
XBRate is a stand-alone BridgeLink application as well as a PGSuper/PGSplice Extension
You can export your pier model from PGSuper/PGSplice to a stand-alone XBRate model
XBRate can be used for many different kinds of piers. The pier defintion does not depend on bridge type.
XBRate supports AASHTO MBE LRFR requirements as well as WSDOT BDM requirements